you see fragmented bones

1069
00:45:20,659 --> 00:45:23,460
now that your eyes begin to adjust.

1070
00:45:25,460 --> 00:45:27,219
And you look up and you see

1071
00:45:28,980 --> 00:45:31,460
this mind-numbing structure.

1072
00:45:31,460 --> 00:45:34,260
All of you begin to exit out into this.

1073
00:45:34,340 --> 00:45:36,740
You see dragons soaring overhead.

1074
00:45:38,900 --> 00:45:43,700
And it looks like it is tangled with bones and rock

1075
