and is blasted up out of the volcano itself.

1076
00:45:51,540 --> 00:45:54,820
The stone and bones look like they've been

1077
00:45:54,820 --> 00:45:58,500
imbued with the dark magic of the nine hells.

1078
00:45:59,060 --> 00:46:03,060
