1079
00:46:03,059 --> 00:46:06,340
with all of its chaotic angles jutting out.

1080
00:46:07,219 --> 00:46:11,219
Within that snarl of cornices and soaring angulation,

1081
00:46:11,219 --> 00:46:14,980
you make out five asymmetric towers

1082
00:46:15,619 --> 00:46:17,860
topped by twisted steeples.

1083
00:46:19,779 --> 00:46:23,380
Screams and roars come from over the edges

1084
00:46:23,380 --> 00:46:26,179
as another blare of the dracorn sounds.

1085
00:46:27,139 --> 00:46:31,139
And you are looking at the temple of Tiamat.

